org.wildfly.security.keystore

Class FilteringKeyStoreSpi

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.security.KeyStoreSpi
      • org.wildfly.security.keystore.DelegatingKeyStoreSpi
        • org.wildfly.security.keystore.FilteringKeyStoreSpi

  • class FilteringKeyStoreSpi
extends DelegatingKeyStoreSpi
    A delegating key store implementation that allows for a predicate to be supplied to filter which aliases will actually be returned.
    Author:
    Darran Lofthouse
